'll help by putting the power of Big Data within everyone\'s reach.','Our Global Leadership Team','','inherit','closed','closed','','7-revision-v1','','','2018-11-06 08:52:12','2018-11-06 08:52:12','',7,'http://localhost:8888/growbydata/2018/11/06/7-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(24,2,'2018-11-06 11:51:40','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Home','','draft','closed','closed','','','','','2018-11-06 11:51:40','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://localhost:8888/growbydata/?p=24',1,'nav_menu_item','',0),(25,2,'2018-11-06 11:51:40','0000-00-00 00:00:00',' ','','','draft','closed','closed','','','','','2018-11-06 11:51:40','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://localhost:8888/growbydata/?p=25',1,'nav_menu_item','',0),(26,2,'2018-11-06 11:51:40','0000-00-00 00:00:00',' ','','','draft','closed','closed','','','','','2018-11-06 11:51:40','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://localhost:8888/growbydata/?p=26',1,'nav_menu_item','',0),(31,2,'2018-11-13 13:34:29','2018-11-13 13:34:29','<div class=\"form-group\">\r\n[text* your-name class:form-control placeholder \"Full Name\"]\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"form-group\">\r\n[url* website class:form-control placeholder \"website\"]\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"form-group\">\r\n[email* your-email class:form-control placeholder \"Email\"]\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"form-group\">\r\n[text* your-phone class:form-control placeholder \"Phone Number\"]\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"form-group\">\r\n[textarea* your-message 10x3 class:form-control placeholder \"Message\"]\r\n</div>\r\n[honeypot email-781][honeypot email-781][honeypot email-781]\r\n[submit \"SUBMIT\"]\n1\nGrowbydata \"[your-subject]\"\n[your-name] <sysadmin@growbydata.com>\nsysadmin@growbydata.com\nFrom: [your-name] \r\nEmail:[your-email]\r\nSubject: [your-subject]\r\n\r\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on Growbydata.com(Request Your Free Trial)\nReply-To: [your-email]\n\n\n\n\nGrowbydata \"[your-subject]\"\nGrowbydata <msubedi@growbydata.com>\n[your-email]\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on Growbydata (http://localhost:8888/growbydata)\nReply-To: msubedi@growbydata.com\n\n\n\nThank you for your message. It has been sent.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nOne or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nYou must accept the terms and conditions before sending your message.\nThe field is required.\nThe field is too long.\nThe field is too short.\nThe date format is incorrect.\nThe date is before the earliest one allowed.\nThe date is after the latest one allowed.\nThere was an unknown error uploading the file.\nYou are not allowed to upload files of this type.\nThe file is too big.\nThere was an error uploading the file.\nThe number format is invalid.\nThe number is smaller than the minimum allowed.\nThe number is larger than the maximum allowed.\nThe answer to the quiz is incorrect.\nYour entered code is incorrect.\nThe e-mail address entered is invalid.\nThe URL is invalid.\nThe telephone number is invalid.','Request Your Free Trial','','publish','closed','closed','','contact-form-1','','','2018-12-03 12:30:05','2018-12-03 12:30:05','',0,'http://localhost:8888/growbydata/?post_type=wpcf7_contact_form&#038;p=31',0,'wpcf7_contact_form','',0),(39,2,'2018-11-13 14:57:58','2018-11-13 14:57:58','GrowByData is looking for motivated <strong>Associate Software Engineer</strong> to join our Team. The right candidates will learn new and developing technologies while supporting our existing Team and will look forward to building a long career with our growing, exciting global company.\r\n\r\n<strong class=\"title\">Requirements</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Good communication skills in English; both Spoken and Written.</li>\r\n 	<li>1+ year of experience in relevant field would be preferable.</li>\r\n 	<li>Skills in PHP and any PHP frameworks such as Laravel, FatFree, Wordpress, etc. would be preferable.</li>\r\n 	<li>Must have skills in HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript (like: jQuery, Regular Expression, Ajax)</li>\r\n 	<li>Knowledge in MySQL databases.</li>\r\n 	<li>Knowledge in Analytics like google analytics, google Adwords, Facebook pixel and Bing would be plus.</li>\r\n 	<li>Knowledge in SEO and PPC marketing would be preferred.</li>\r\n 	<li>Prior knowledge in ecommerce platform (such as Big commerce, 3D Cart, Shopify, Magento) would be preferred</li>\r\n 	<li>Knowledge in GIT/SVN version control system.</li>\r\n 	<li>Passionate about learning new technology and self-motivated / Self-driven to contribute ideas and share knowledge proactively / Must be a team player.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong class=\"title\">Responsibilities</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Service installations and bug fixing/maintenance task on stores with various ecommerce platforms (Yahoo, BigCommerce, 3dCart, Magento, Volusion, MivaMerchant)</li>\r\n 	<li>SEO content management (like: 301 redirects, canonical, noindex, content implementation, Ads/remarketing implementation</li>\r\n 	<li>Reliably estimate time expectations and co-ordinate with other teams in the company for prioritization and related bugs and features</li>\r\n 	<li>Maintain strict confidentiality of your work</li>\r\n 	<li>Excel under tight deadlines, and proactively communicate with team members and managers</li>\r\n 	<li>Communicate proactively and effectively with team members, leads, management, and clients where necessary</li>\r\n 	<li>Understand existing support practices and assist the team.</li>\r\n 	<li>Assist in creating a friendly, entrepreneurial and A+ corporate culture in Nepal</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong class=\"title\">Education: Minimum B.E Computer Science, Information Science or equivalent</strong><strong class=\"title\">Experience: Prior one-year experience in a relevant field would be preferred and favorable</strong>\r\n\r\nThe right candidate will be looking for not just a new job, but a stellar career with our growing company. If you want to leave your mark on a new endeavor, and really take ownership of what will be the driving force of a successful company, then let us know you want to become a part of our team! <a href=\"mailto:inquiries@growbydata.com\">inquiries@growbydata.com</a> to be considered immediately.','ASSOCIATE SOFTWARE ENGINEER','','publish','closed','closed','','associate-software-engineer','','','2018-11-13 16:12:22','2018-11-13 16:12:22','',0,'http://localhost:8888/growbydata/?post_type=jobs&#038;p=39',0,'jobs','',0),(40,2,'2018-11-13 14:57:58','2018-11-13 14:57:58','GrowByData is looking for motivated <strong>Associate Software Engineer</strong> to join our Team. The right candidates will learn new and developing technologies while supporting our existing Team and will look forward to building a long career with our growing, exciting global company.\r\n\r\n<strong class=\"title\">Requirements</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Good communication skills in English; both Spoken and Written.</li>\r\n 	<li>1+ year of experience in relevant field would be preferable.</li>\r\n 	<li>Skills in PHP and any PHP frameworks such as Laravel, FatFree, Wordpress, etc. would be preferable.</li>\r\n 	<li>Must have skills in HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript (like: jQuery, Regular Expression, Ajax)</li>\r\n 	<li>Knowledge in MySQL databases.</li>\r\n 	<li>Knowledge in Analytics like google analytics, google Adwords, Facebook pixel and Bing would be plus.</li>\r\n 	<li>Knowledge in SEO and PPC marketing would be preferred.</li>\r\n 	<li>Prior knowledge in ecommerce platform (such as Big commerce, 3D Cart, Shopify, Magento) would be preferred</li>\r\n 	<li>Knowledge in GIT/SVN version control system.</li>\r\n 	<li>Passionate about learning new technology and self-motivated / Self-driven to contribute ideas and share knowledge proactively / Must be a team player.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong class=\"title\">Responsibilities</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Service installations and bug fixing/maintenance task on stores with various ecommerce platforms (Yahoo, BigCommerce, 3dCart, Magento, Volusion, MivaMerchant)</li>\r\n 	<li>SEO content management (like: 301 redirects, canonical, noindex, content implementation, Ads/remarketing implementation</li>\r\n 	<li>Reliably estimate time expectations and co-ordinate with other teams in the company for prioritization and related bugs and features</li>\r\n 	<li>Maintain strict confidentiality of your work</li>\r\n 	<li>Excel under tight deadlines, and proactively communicate with team members and managers</li>\r\n 	<li>Communicate proactively and effectively with team members, leads, management, and clients where necessary</li>\r\n 	<li>Understand existing support practices and assist the team.</li>\r\n 	<li>Assist in creating a friendly, entrepreneurial and A+ corporate culture in Nepal</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong class=\"title\">Education: Minimum B.E Computer Science, Information Science or equivalent</strong><strong class=\"title\">Experience: Prior one-year experience in a relevant field would be preferred and favorable</strong>\r\n\r\nThe right candidate will be looking for not just a new job, but a stellar career with our growing company. If you want to leave your mark on a new endeavor, and really take ownership of what will be the driving force of a successful company, then let us know you want to become a part of our team! <a href=\"mailto:inquiries@growbydata.com\">inquiries@growbydata.com</a> to be considered immediately.','ASSOCIATE SOFTWARE ENGINEER','','inherit','closed','closed','','39-revision-v1','','','2018-11-13 14:57:58','2018-11-13 14:57:58','',39,'http://localhost:8888/growbydata/39-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(41,2,'2018-11-13 15:04:42','2018-11-13 15:04:42','We’re building a global company that puts the power of Big Data within everyone’s\r\nreach. We recruit the best people, help them grow, and invest in their happiness.','Why work at GrowByData?','','publish','closed','closed','','career-overview','','','2018-11-15 05:54:08','2018-11-15 05:54:08','',0,'http://localhost:8888/growbydata/?page_id=41',0,'page','',0),(42,2,'2018-11-13 15:04:42','2018-11-13 15:04:42','We’re building a global company that puts the power of Big Data within everyone’s\r\nreach. We recruit the best people, help them grow, and invest in their happiness.','Why work at GrowByData?','','inherit','closed','closed','','41-revision-v1','','','2018-11-13 15:04:42','2018-11-13 15:04:42','',41,'http://localhost:8888/growbydata/41-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(43,2,'2018-11-13 15:43:21','2018-11-13 15:43:21','GrowByData is looking for an experienced <strong>Software Engineer</strong> to join the Team! The individual will be responsible for designing, implementing, and monitoring complex software systems.\r\n\r\n<strong class=\"title\">Requirements</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Good understanding of computer software, databases, and programming</li>\r\n 	<li>Comprehensive understanding of web development and best practices</li>\r\n 	<li>Must have worked extensively in the Programming Languages - (PHP, JavaScript, jQuery).</li>\r\n 	<li>Experienced with Laravel 5+ framework</li>\r\n 	<li>Familiar with REST API using Passport and other authentication techniques</li>\r\n 	<li>Must have experience working with databases such as MySQL, MSSQL PgSQL etc</li>\r\n 	<li>Should have strong grasp of database concepts like stored procedures, triggers, functions, indexing and query optimization etc.</li>\r\n 	<li>Experienced with version control management (Git, Bitbucket) to maintain code, documentation and configurations</li>\r\n 	<li>Basic idea of UNIX and web server handling in AWS platforms</li>\r\n 	<li>Experience of working on different E-Commerce Platforms (Magento, Yahoo, Big Commerce, 3D Cart, Shopify Plus etc.) is preferred</li>\r\n 	<li>Knowledge/Experience with Business Intelligence tools (Jaspersoft, Pentaho etc.) is preferred</li>\r\n 	<li>Knowledge of Big Data (Amazon Redshift, Hadoop) is preferred</li>\r\n 	<li>Good communication skills in English and Nepali</li>\r\n 	<li>Willing to work off-hours preferred</li>\r\n 	<li>Experience with micro services, n-layered application, design patterns, SQL, design patterns, concurrency patterns is preferred</li>\r\n 	<li>Knowledge of code optimization, query optimization, code refactoring and test-driven development will be a plus point</li>\r\n 	<li>Familiar with first- and third-party cookies and its limitations</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong class=\"title\">Responsibilities</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Will be required to code and debug software modules while following industry standard development practices and coding conventions</li>\r\n 	<li>Will be required to model and develop database artifacts such as tables, views, store procedures, triggers etc.</li>\r\n 	<li>Provide technical guidance in software design and development activities</li>\r\n 	<li>Perform key role in cross-functional teams through development, testing, and product launch</li>\r\n 	<li>Be a persistent, creative problem solver and remain cool and effective in a crisis</li>\r\n 	<li>Document and demonstrate solutions by developing documentation, flowcharts, layouts, diagrams, charts, code comments and clear code</li>\r\n 	<li>Excel under tight deadlines, and proactively communicate with team members and managers</li>\r\n 	<li>Many more as the right candidate grows and contribute</li>\r\n 	<li>Communicate proactively and effectively with team members leads, management, and clients</li>\r\n 	<li>Maintain strict confidentiality of your work</li>\r\n 	<li>Assist in creating a friendly, entrepreneurial and A+ corporate culture in Nepal</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong class=\"title\">Education: Minimum B.E Computer Science, Information Science or equivalent</strong><strong class=\"title\">Experience: Prior 3 years and above experience in a relevant field would be preferred and favorable.</strong>\r\n\r\nThe right candidate will be looking for not just a new job, but a stellar career with our growing company. Ideal candidate should be a self-driven, motivated and an innovative engineer with the never filling appetite to learn. If you want to leave your mark on a new endeavor, and really take ownership of what will be the driving force of a successful company, then let us know you want to become a part of our team! Email <a href=\"mailto:inquiries@growbydata.com\">inquiries@growbydata.com</a> to be considered immediately.','SOFTWARE ENGINEER','','publish','closed','closed','','software-engineer','','','2018-11-16 06:35:41','2018-11-16 06:35:41','',0,'http://localhost:8888/growbydata/?post_type=jobs&#038;p=43',1,'jobs','',0),(44,2,'2018-11-13 15:43:21','2018-11-13 15:43:21','GrowByData is looking for an experienced<strong>Software Engineer</strong> to join the Team! The individual will be responsible for designing, implementing, and monitoring complex software systems.\r\n\r\n<strong class=\"title\">Requirements</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Good understanding of computer software, databases, and programming</li>\r\n 	<li>Comprehensive understanding of web development and best practices</li>\r\n 	<li>Must have worked extensively in the Programming Languages - (PHP, JavaScript, jQuery).</li>\r\n 	<li>Experienced with Laravel 5+ framework</li>\r\n 	<li>Familiar with REST API using Passport and other authentication techniques</li>\r\n 	<li>Must have experience working with databases such as MySQL, MSSQL PgSQL etc</li>\r\n 	<li>Should have strong grasp of database concepts like stored procedures, triggers, functions, indexing and query optimization etc.</li>\r\n 	<li>Experienced with version control management (Git, Bitbucket) to maintain code, documentation and configurations</li>\r\n 	<li>Basic idea of UNIX and web server handling in AWS platforms</li>\r\n 	<li>Experience of working on different E-Commerce Platforms (Magento, Yahoo, Big Commerce, 3D Cart, Shopify Plus etc.) is 